### ===== PUBLIC ANIME ENDPOINTS =====

### 1. Get Trending Anime
GET http://localhost:8080/api/anime/trending?page=0&size=5

### 2. Search Anime by Name
GET http://localhost:8080/api/anime/search?q=Naruto&page=0&size=5

### 3. Search with Empty Query (should return 400)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/anime/search?q=

### 4. Get Anime by MAL ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/anime/21

### 5. Get Anime by Invalid ID (should return 500)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/anime/99999999

### 6. Get Seasonal Anime
GET http://localhost:8080/api/anime/seasonal?page=0&size=5

### 7. Filter Anime by Genre
GET http://localhost:8080/api/anime/filter?genres=1,2&order_by=score&sort=desc&page=0&size=5


### ===== AUTH ENDPOINTS =====

### 8. Register a New User
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Test User",
    "email": "testuser@example.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

### 9. Resend Verification Email
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/resend-verification
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "testuser@example.com"
}

### 10. Verify Email (copy token from DB/logs and replace below)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/auth/verify?token=REPLACE_WITH_ACTUAL_TOKEN

### 11. Login as User
# @name userLogin
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "testuser@example.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

### 12. Login as Admin
# @name adminLogin
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "admin@animesite.com",
    "password": "admin123"
}

### 13. Refresh Token
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "refreshToken": "REPLACE_WITH_REFRESH_TOKEN"
}

### 14. Logout
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "refreshToken": "REPLACE_WITH_REFRESH_TOKEN"
}

### 15. Forgot Password
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "testuser@example.com"
}

### 16. Reset Password
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "token": "REPLACE_WITH_RESET_TOKEN",
    "newPassword": "newPassword456"
}


### ===== USER PROFILE =====

### 17. Get My Profile
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/me
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 18. Update Profile
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/user/me
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
    "name": "Updated Name"
}

### 19. Change Password
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/user/me/password
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
    "currentPassword": "password123",
    "newPassword": "newPassword456"
}

### 20. Delete Account
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/user/me
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}


### ===== REVIEWS =====

### 21. Add Review (replace ANIME_ID, e.g. 21)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/anime/21/review
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
    "starRating": 5,
    "comment": "Amazing anime! Highly recommend."
}

### 22. Get Reviews for an Anime (public)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/anime/21/reviews?page=0&size=10

### 23. Edit Review (replace REVIEW_ID)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/reviews/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
    "starRating": 4,
    "comment": "Updated review comment."
}

### 24. Delete Own Review (replace REVIEW_ID)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/reviews/1
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}


### ===== WATCHLIST =====

### 25. Add to Watchlist
POST http://localhost:8080/api/watchlist
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
    "animeId": 1,
    "status": "PLAN_TO_WATCH"
}

### 26. Get My Watchlist
GET http://localhost:8080/api/watchlist
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 27. Update Watchlist Status (replace WATCHLIST_ID)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/watchlist/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
    "status": "WATCHING"
}

### 28. Remove from Watchlist (replace WATCHLIST_ID)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/watchlist/1
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}


### ===== FAVORITES =====

### 29. Add to Favorites
POST http://localhost:8080/api/favorites/21
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 30. Get My Favorites
GET http://localhost:8080/api/favorites
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### 31. Remove from Favorites
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/favorites/21
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}


### ===== ADMIN ENDPOINTS =====

### 32. List All Users
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 33. Delete User (replace USER_ID)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/admin/users/2
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 34. Set Affiliate URL
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/admin/anime/1/affiliate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
    "affiliateUrl": "https://www.crunchyroll.com/series/..."
}

### 35. Delete Anime (cascades reviews/watchlist/favorites)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/admin/anime/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 36. Delete Any Review (replace REVIEW_ID)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/admin/review/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}


### ===== NEWS =====

### 37. Get All News (public)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/news?page=0&size=10

### 38. Create News Article (admin)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/news
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
    "title": "New Anime Season Announced",
    "content": "Exciting new anime series for the upcoming season...",
    "imageUrl": "https://example.com/image.jpg"
}

### 39. Update News (admin, replace NEWS_ID)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/news/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
    "title": "Updated Title",
    "content": "Updated content..."
}

### 40. Delete News (admin, replace NEWS_ID)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/news/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
